	* doc/make.texi (Goals): [SV 51306] Improve MAKECMDGOALS example

2022-08-07  Dmitry Goncharov  <dgoncharov@users.sf.net>

	* doc/make.texi (Remaking Makefiles): [SV 61623] Add optimization

